            "value": "¡Estás fisiológicamente listo para este objetivo!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Je bent weer op de goede weg. Volg het schema van de coach om je doel te halen.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du bist wieder auf Kurs. Folge dem Plan des Coaches, um dein Ziel zu erreichen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You're back on track. Follow the coach's plan to reach your goal."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vuelves a ir por buen camino. Sigue el plan del entrenador para lograr tu objetivo."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Je gesprekken gaan rechtstreeks naar je gekozen AI-provider — niet via onze servers. Je houdt zelf de controle over kosten, model en privacy.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Deine Gespräche gehen direkt an deinen gewählten KI-Anbieter — nicht über unsere Server. Du behältst die Kontrolle über Kosten, Modell und Privatsphäre."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your conversations go directly to your chosen AI provider — not through our servers. You stay in control of cost, model and privacy."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tus conversaciones van directamente a tu proveedor de IA elegido — no a través de nuestros servidores. Mantienes el control sobre el coste, el modelo y la privacidad."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Je kunt de sleutel zelf later invoeren in Instellingen.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du kannst den Schlüssel später selbst in den Einstellungen eingeben."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You can enter the key yourself later in Settings."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Puedes introducir la clave tú mismo más tarde en Ajustes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Je TRIMP deze week (%@) ligt achter op het weekdoel (%@). Pak de geplande trainingen op.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dein TRIMP diese Woche (%1$@) liegt hinter dem Wochenziel (%2$@). Nimm die geplanten Trainings auf."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your TRIMP this week (%1$@) is behind the weekly goal (%2$@). Pick up the planned workouts."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tu TRIMP esta semana (%1$@) está por detrás del objetivo semanal (%2$@). Retoma los entrenamientos planificados."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Je TRIMP deze week (%1$@) ligt achter op het weekdoel (%2$@). Pak de geplande trainingen op."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Je Vibe Score is %@/100 — je lichaam is uitgeput. **%@** (TRIMP: %@) was zwaarder dan je herstel toelaat. Neem rust.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dein Vibe Score ist %1$@/100 — dein Körper ist erschöpft. **%2$@** (TRIMP: %3$@) war härter, als deine Erholung zulässt. Ruh dich aus."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your Vibe Score is %1$@/100 — your body is exhausted. **%2$@** (TRIMP: %3$@) was heavier than your recovery allows. Take rest."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tu Vibe Score es %1$@/100 — tu cuerpo está agotado. **%2$@** (TRIMP: %3$@) fue más exigente de lo que tu recuperación permite. Descansa."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Je Vibe Score is %1$@/100 — je lichaam is uitgeput. **%2$@** (TRIMP: %3$@) was zwaarder dan je herstel toelaat. Neem rust."
          }
        }
      }
    },
